text: Beautiful Freehold Condominium with luscious greenery. Walking distance to MRT too.Low rise and low density blocks with private lifts. Good size units here.

The performance of violin + guitar and Sheila spontaneous without rehearsing. They played for their first time yesterday. Only our Lord is the conductor that can orchestrated such beautiful song. 3 of them met for the first time and performed together for Inspired ! As audience you can never guess! But with our Lord He is the conductor that make each of us play our instrument as He guides us, the music will be beautiful just like what happened yesterday.üôè

Quiet and peaceful environment with beautiful landscaped swimming pools and gardens.

Marble and real wood parquet floors given the interiors a luxurious feel and the built-in wine chiller is a nice finishing touch.

For those who drive, each dwelling gets a private lift lobby coming up from the car park. For those who don't, a shuttle bus runs 21 times per day from the development. It goes to the nearest MRT station and also to Coronation Plaza where there is a supermarket and a few eateries.
Beautiful condo, mostly families with small kids. Great view, excellent common areas and nicely designed apartments
It took me 25 minutes to slow walk to the condo.  On the way there, it's not wheelchair friendly. This is a very posh place .
